{"type":"message","id":"49d58021","parentId":"a50e33a3","timestamp":"2026-04-04T02:08:34.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. I've gathered the information. Let me summarize for the user.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nClaude Code 当前使用的配置（从 `~/.openclaw/claude.env`）：\n\n| 配置项 | 值 |\n|--------|-----|\n| **模型** | `minimax-m2.5` |\n| **API 地址** | `https://zhenze-huhehaote.cmecloud.cn/api/coding` |\n\n直接运行 `claude` CLI 时，需要先 `source ~/.openclaw/claude.env` 才会使用这个配置。否则它会尝试连接 Anthropic 官方 API（没有 API Key 会失败）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":19491,"output":125,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19616,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775268512331,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3d1e057a-c11b-4b60-a412-cc40847987bc"}}
